    "English": "A specialist <span class=\"name name-technology\">biological catalysation device</span>.<br><br>This unit takes advantage of naturally occurring enzymes in order to facilitate increased energy yields and faster processing in a wide range of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
