  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Amino Chamber from <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Metal Plating</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Chlorine</span>.<br><br>Craft <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Metal Plating</span> from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite</span> or purchase at a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Trade Terminal</span>.<br>Refine Condensed Carbon from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon</span>. Condensed Carbon can occasionally be found as crystals on planet surfaces.<br>Refine Chlorine from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span>, which is harvested from <span class=\"name name-technology\">underwater mineral deposits</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金属电镀</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氯</span>制作氨基舱。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体</span>制作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">微处理器</span>或从<span class=\"name name-technology\">交易终端</span>购买。<br>从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>中精炼浓缩碳。浓缩碳偶尔会以结晶形式出现在行星表面。<br>用提取自<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下矿床</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>精炼氯。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金屬電鍍</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氯</span>製作胺基艙。<br><br><span class=\"name name-commodity\">金屬電鍍</span>可用<span class=\"name name-earth\">鐵氧體</span>製成，或在<span class=\"name name-technology\">交易終端站</span>購買。<br>濃縮碳可由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>精製而成。濃縮碳偶爾也會以結晶形式出現在星球表面。<br>將<span class=\"name name-technology\">水底礦資源產地</span>所採收的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>精製成氯。"
  },
